Action Replay Cheats
--------------------       __
Compiled by /\/asty Boy & _/aybee


 Load the specified game,then freeze the action.
 Type M immediatly followed by one of the given addresses. eg. M6529
 (Paperboy).You will be then presented by a row of numbers looking like:
 
   06 00 99 33 33 22 43 22 11 33

 Only alter the FIRST number or the game may crash.Just pop in a new number
 such as 99 and when you jump back into the game (by pressing X) you will
 have a nice supply of lives! Just like pokeing on the 64 really.
 

